[DESCRIPTION]
\fBarki-maint\fP performs maintenance operations on datasets.

Each maintenance operation has its own subcommand, allowing to work on datasets
and segments as needed.

[EXAMPLES]
Here are some example invocations of \fBarki-maint\fP:
.P
.nf
  # Unarchive segments from 2022
  arki-maint unarchive dataset/.archive/last/2022-*.grib
.fi
